Summary: Oval UFO caught on iPhone photograph
divs: Sighting DetailsWhile driving on Route 25 north towards Trumbull, I was taking a few pictures to show the hues of the leaves to friend. Nothing was noticed in the pictures at the time. However, when looking at the pictures on the iPhone a oval dark shape is present traveling from left to right in the sky. I do not recall seeing any birds flying by at that time since it was very cold and windy outside. See attached images for details.
